Are you running the latest version of TensorFlow?

Regardless, if you look at the bottom after the "unknown op" messages, it is printing the expected result: b'Hello, TensorFlow!' It looks like you're only missing ops for building decision trees, so you should still be able to run (most) TensorFlow models successfully.

body:
Are you running the latest version of TensorFlow?

Regardless, if you look at the bottom after the "unknown op" messages, it is printing the expected result: `b'Hello, TensorFlow!'` It looks like you're only missing ops for building decision trees, so you should still be able to run (most) TensorFlow models successfully.
